commit message:
Add Lithuanian layout

Contributed by mgedmin, with double quotes added to the 5-row layout.

See https://code.google.com/p/hackerskeyboard/issues/detail?id=188
Bump version, new version code scheme including minor version.

English 5-row: remove redundant altchars.

The layout had repeated the main and shifted chars, this is
no longer necessary and is confusing when it's used as basis
for derived layouts.

Fix crash for multitouch on popup keyboard.

Patch provided by host127001, thank you!

See https://code.google.com/p/hackerskeyboard/issues/detail?id=380
